      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Everyone who was offered a free slot will receive CoB bonded chips for free (as discussed with Tim). However, it is unclear how many bonded chips you will receive, and you may be able to get more if you pay a little extra.\n\nA pack of open source chips would be interesting :)\nHowever, it would probably be without the host-PCBs, since wafer.space only bonds the chips to the CoB PCB.",
      "author": {
        "id": "323371864074485771",
        "name": "mole99",
        "discriminator": "0000",
        "nickname": "Leo Moser (mole99)",
        "color": null,
        "isBot": false,
